HEADWORD: Oreopteris
<hw>Oreopteris</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>A genus of ferns having
species, formerly included in genus <gen>Dryopteris</gen> or
<gen>Thelypteris</gen>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> genus <gen>Oreopteris</gen>.</syn>⟦br⟧
